NAIC_CODE.instruction: NAIC code of the insurance carrier

POLICY_NUMBER.instruction: Policy number assigned by the carrier

GARAGE_ADDRESS.instruction: Address that includes street zipcode county where vehicle is primarily garaged

VEHICLE_USE Business.instruction: Whether the vehicle is used for business purposes

VEHICLE_USE PLEASURE.instruction: Whether the vehicle is used for pleasure

VEHICLE_USE COMML.instruction: Whether the vehicle is used for commercial purposes

VEHICLE_USE RETAIL.instruction: Whether the vehicle is used for retail delivery

VEHICLE_USE SERVICE.instruction: Whether the vehicle is used for service

VEHICLE_USE FARM.instruction: Whether the vehicle is used for farming

VEHICLE_Coverage LIAB.instruction: Whether the vehicle has Liablity Coverage

VEHICLE_Coverage NoFault.instruction: Whether the vehicle had No Fault

VEHICLE_Coverage ADDNL NoFault.instruction: Whether the vehicle had Additional No Fault

VEHICLE_Coverage MED PAY.instruction: Whether the vehicle has medical pay

VEHICLE_Coverage UNINS MOTOR.instruction: Whether the vehicle has Uninsured Motor Coverage

VEHICLE_Coverage UNDRINS MOTOR.instruction: Whether the vehicle has Under insured Motor Coverage

VEHICLE_Coverage Towing & Labor.instruction: Whether the vehicle has Towing and Labor Coverage

VEHICLE_Coverage SPEC C OF L.instruction: Whether the vehicle has specified list of causes of loss

VEHICLE_Coverage F.instruction: Whether the vehicle covers specified Cause of Loss by Fire

VEHICLE_Coverage FT.instruction: Whether the vehicle covers specified Causes of Loss by Fire and Theft

VEHICLE_Coverage SPEC FTW.instruction: Whether the vehicle covers specified Causes of Loss by Fire Theft and Windstorm

VEHICLE_Coverage LSP.instruction: Whether the vehicle covers limited Specified Peril

VEHICLE_Coverage COMP OTC.instruction: Whether the vehicle has Comprehensive Other Than Collision physical damage coverages

VEHICLE_Coverage COLL.instruction: Whether the vehicle has collision coverage

VEHICLE_Coverage RENT REIMB.instruction: Whether the vehicle has rent reimbursement

VEHICLE_Deductibles AA.instruction: Whether the vehicle has agreed deductibles

VEHICLE_Deductibles ACV.instruction: Whether the vehicle has actual cash value deductibles

VEHICLE_Deductibles COMP OTC.instruction: Whether the vehicle has Comprehensive or Other Than Collision physical damage deductibles

VEHICLE_Deductibles SPEC C OR L.instruction: Whether the vehicle has  Specified Cause of Loss deductibles

VEHICLE_Deductibles amount.instruction: Amount of deductible in dollars for example 1000

VEHICLE_Deductible amount collision.instruction: amount of deductible in dollars for example 1000 COLL
